Class PartialExecution

java.lang.Object
org.apache.wayang.core.platform.PartialExecution
public class PartialExecution extends Object

      public PartialExecution(long measuredExecutionTime, double lowerCost, double upperCost, Collection<ExecutionLineageNode> executionLineageNodes, Configuration configuration)
      Creates a new instance.
      Parameters:
      measuredExecutionTime - the time measured for the partial execution
      lowerCost - the lower possible costs for the new instance (excluding fix costs)
      upperCost - the upper possible costs for the new instance (excluding fix costs)
      executionLineageNodes - for all executed ExecutionOperators
      configuration - the Configuration to re-estimate execution statistics
